{"tid":2464291,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜濤遭TVB記者會惡搞　姜濤稱馮盈盈林盛斌不需道歉：好小事！","createTime":"2021-03-27T10:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T11:20:30.000Z","uid":350584,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"176afbd7e1c545a472fa0df071b48a5854b1ca3c","tid":2464291,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:48:20.000Z","msg":"無綫日前舉行記招介紹九大新綜藝節目，鄧智堅在活動上帶着金色假髮自稱「薑蓉」，惡搞人氣男團MIRROR成員姜濤，隨即惹來大量「姜糖」不滿。姜濤今日（27/3）現身演唱會記者會時亦有為事件作出回應：「希望大家以輕鬆心情去睇呢件事，都唔係好大件事，Artist都係為咗令人開心，所以我冇任何介意。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdMVr3imBdFYDTkQ9FD9rg3pXzory8Fg797FAaEv2Xbgb?filename=P6SMDiY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6SMDiY.jpg&h=aee8e96b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa627a9c0e34c1fb545a1e0ff02d7bcd3ef1ea78","tid":2464291,"uid":350584,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:48:39.000Z","msg":"身後的MIRROR成員柳應廷（Jer）笑言：「姜濤真係紅，以前我哋都模仿四大天王。」姜濤立即謙虛否認，對於有粉絲湧入馮盈盈等人的社交網留言炮轟，他亦為此激動行為致歉：「希望藉住呢件事令更加多人留意MIRROR，Fans有部分會激動啲，同大家講聲唔好意思。（有冇留意馮盈盈、Bob出Po道歉？）唔需要，好小事，未到要道歉。我都代我Fans同大家講聲唔好意思，打和。」另外，經理人花姐（黃慧君）同樣認為一眾藝人毋須就事件致歉：「其實未去到要道歉嘅，我諗每一個藝人出嚟扮嘢又好，其實都係想娛樂觀眾。」"},{"pid":"ad8ebb1582110d07c3efbddcd662c988e7141b91","tid":2464291,"uid":350584,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUL6fKfQWWRyG3iFK8cuU5TRy8kqoVVhMhzzWP1NvVMuq?filename=zhqa4Zx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzhqa4Zx.jpg&h=ee7233d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d041fe01df85d8309f3bbcc396e884576dc518b8","tid":2464291,"uid":350584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5wOFzHNAjJAKsLOCHtKJn16tVs0=/487x273/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XYX5XY6GQZHC5DWEUECX3NK324.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3