:51:59.000Z","msg":"姜b 有班小丑幫佢蹭熱度不知幾開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"279789e5d96d26ca32be970913d56dae27fb34e9","tid":2464291,"uid":57036,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"Mirror舉辦演唱會之際<br />\n竟然得到隔離台無私宣傳<br />\n實屬難得"},{"pid":"c4ff6f6a6f79ab2db204bcb4a501a6bf5f918d63","tid":2464291,"uid":78613,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"姜一直以外對外既回應都幾得體<br />\nRespect 抵佢紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51c52974e0058662cd50644776b888979f45ad1","tid":2464291,"uid":350584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"13cba37bf2b857f2f2fe94ab3c6c4b9c90ff0cd5","tid":2464291,"uid":121504,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"花姐比個下台階比得好靚<br />\n女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"TVB記招惡搞姜濤　花姐稱毋須道歉：好開心隔籬台留意我哋動態"},{"pid":"2169096086e711fedeb1fd7a4b2824850431dd2c","tid":2464291,"uid":350584,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:57:31.000Z","msg":"經理人花姐（黃慧君）今日（27/3）現身MIRROR演唱會記招現場，她接受《香港01》訪問時指，自己沒有認真看過整段演出，但認為一眾藝人毋須就事件致歉：「其實未去到要道歉嘅，我諗每一個藝人出嚟扮嘢又好，或者做各類型嘅表演都好，其實都係想娛樂觀眾啫。可能佢哋會覺得『你扮得姜濤唔好睇』，但係我哋應該尊重每個藝人嘅表演。」"},{"pid":"63513df8a2d88f9fa7faa3d58e3b6c87f010eace","tid":2464291,"uid":350584,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:58:14.000Z","msg":"談到當中的對白，花姐認為純屬搞笑，亦指姜濤沒有為這件事感到不高興：「姜濤同我睇完都喺度笑，唔會嬲囉，因為大家都知呢啲嘢都係講笑啫，唔需要咁認真。反而我好開心，我哋留意隔籬台嘅動態，隔籬台都會留意我哋嘅動態，咁唔係更加好咩？」花姐又希望一眾「姜糖」不要太緊張，相信友台前輩都會愛錫姜濤，不需要將這件事看得太重。"},{"pid":"2063afeabc4eef1af1ed1b331396cc402a809ef1","tid":2464291,"uid":379823,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"以一個出道無耐既藝人黎講真係好識撈，非常大方得體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"239eae85171a754b36c492d3b6ce08863011883a","tid":2464291,"uid":11676,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4ff6f6a6f79ab2db204bcb4a501a6bf5f918d63","tid":2464291,"uid":78613,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"姜一直以外對外既回應都幾得體<br />\nRespect 抵佢紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"點都有人教路"},{"pid":"45f7f7b2adbeec91cfcbc9a5c075805aa91eb333","tid":2464291,"uid":71657,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T11:00:40.000Z","msg":"姜呢下高質 <br />\n又畀到下台階人哋<br />\n又得到世人讚賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fafe2a37502ef36f3245120ba660264b95d53216","tid":2464291,"uid":350584,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"239eae85171a754b36c492d3b6ce08863011883a","tid":2464291,"uid":11676,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4ff6f6a6f79ab2db204bcb4a501a6bf5f918d63","tid":2464291,"uid":78613,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:53:56.000Z","msg":"姜一直以外對外既回應都幾得體<br />\nRespect 抵佢紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"點都有人教路"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T11:01:06.000Z","msg":"好多有人教完路都係咁臭串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369602ce42d5f2006701a0aea6e61d84582944ef","tid":2464291,"uid":384851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T11:03:15.000Z","msg":"可能mirror 同花姐本身都冇睇cctvb，喺之後先知覺得好小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cffd8d3ae71269422935cc3ea584cc7aaedc39f","tid":2464291,"uid":168668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"fafe2a37502ef36f3245120ba660264b95d53216","ti